sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as External Client
    participant GW as Gateway<br/>(Envoy/Istio/AgentGW)<br/>80/443 TCP
    participant EPP as EPP<br/>(llm-d-inference-scheduler)<br/>9002/TCP gRPC
    participant Decode as Decode Pod<br/>vLLM :8000/TCP<br/>Sidecar :8200/TCP
    participant Prefill as Prefill Pod<br/>vLLM :8000/TCP<br/>NIXL :5600/TCP
    participant HF as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OTel as OTel Collector<br/>4317/TCP gRPC
    participant Prom as Prometheus<br/>(PodMonitor)

    Note over Client,Decode: Flow 1: Online Inference Request (Standard)
    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS, Auth: Configurable
    GW->>EPP: ext-proc gRPC<br/>9002/TCP, No encryption
    EPP->>Decode: Scrape metrics<br/>GET /metrics :8000/TCP HTTP
    EPP-->>GW: Selected endpoint (Decode pod)
    GW->>Decode: Forward request<br/>HTTP :8000/TCP, No encryption
    Decode-->>Client: HTTP SSE streaming response<br/>Configurable TLS

    Note over Client,Prefill: Flow 2: Disaggregated Prefill/Decode (P/D)
    Client->>GW: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>HTTP/HTTPS
    GW->>EPP: ext-proc gRPC<br/>9002/TCP
    EPP-->>GW: Selected Decode pod
    GW->>Decode: Forward to Decode<br/>HTTP :8200/TCP (routing sidecar)
    Decode->>Prefill: Route to Prefill<br/>HTTP :8000/TCP
    Note over Prefill: Prefill computes KV cache
    Prefill->>Decode: RDMA KV cache transfer<br/>NIXL :5600/TCP<br/>GPU-Direct (IB/RoCE/EFA)
    Note over Decode: Decode generates tokens
    Decode-->>Client: HTTP SSE streaming response

    Note over HF,Decode: Flow 3: Model Loading
    Decode->>HF: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS :443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer HF_TOKEN
    Prefill->>HF: Download model weights<br/>HTTPS :443/TCP, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer HF_TOKEN

    Note over Prom,Decode: Flow 4: Monitoring & Observability
    Prom->>Decode: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP :8000/TCP, 30s interval
    Prom->>Prefill: Scrape /metrics<br/>HTTP :8000/TCP, 30s interval
    Decode->>OTel: Export traces (OTLP)<br/>gRPC :4317/TCP, No encryption
    Prefill->>OTel: Export traces (OTLP)<br/>gRPC :4317/TCP, No encryption
